<DOCNO> NYT20000318.0070 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-18 11:41 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0961 &Cx1f; var-z
u i BC-IRAN-TENSIONS-REVIEW-     03-18 1112
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-IRAN-TENSIONS-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
ITS VOTERS HAVE SPOKEN. NOW MEET IRAN'S GUNMEN. 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
special arrangement only. Asian and European points: contact Karl
Horwitz in Paris for details and prices (Phone: 47 42 17 11; FAX:
47-42-80-44). Latin American points: contact the Los Angeles office
(Phone: 310-996-0075; FAX: 310-996-0089) 
(bl) 
 By JOHN F. BURNS   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
