<SLUG> BC-REVIEW-BUDGET-FINAL-NYT </SLUG>
  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Editors: The following items from The N.Y. Times Week in Review
for Sunday, March 19, moved Saturday.
</P>
<P>
   This final budget adds ECON-STOCKS-REVIEW.
</P>
<P>
   On the dress page:
</P>
<P>
   (Moved in the `a' category)
</P>
<P>
   OIL-POLITICS-REVIEW (Washington) _ OPEC has displayed startling
muscle in the past year, sending oil and gasoline prices soaring.
