<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-18 13:50 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0974 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k BC-KRUGMAN-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      03-18 0751
