<P>
   HRAP-MAIN _ ATLANTA _ News of the day in the search for former
black activist H. Rap Brown, known as Jamil Abdullah Al-Amin. One
sheriff's deputy was shot and killed and another wounded Thursday
night while trying to deliver a warrant against Brown. (Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). MOVED
