   CYBERCRIME _ WASHINGTON _ A new Justice Department report on
cybercrime puts Attorney General Janet Reno in the center of a
battle between cops who seek more powerful Internet policing tools
and critics who see the study as a threat to online privacy.
(Glass, Cox News Service).
</P>
<P>
   EDs: MOVED Thursday in (w) Washington and (f) financial
categories.
</P>
<P>
   BOTBALL _ RESTON, Va. _ Engineers, scientists and ecstatic
Botball fans roared in the bleachers as foot-high robots created by
teens and pre-teens stampeded across a white tabletop. ``If every
science classroom had this level of enthusiasm, we'd be turning out
world-class scientists by the dozens,'' said Lou Mayo, a planetary
scientist who works for Raytheon Corp. at the Goddard Space Flight
Center. His firm is one of many testing the notion that Botball and
other techno-sports can entice the next generation of workers to
study more science and math. (Mollison, Cox News Service). WITH
PHOTOS.
</P>
