contestants on CBS' Survivor start cannibalizing each other
(figuratively) until summer. But it's not too late to start rooting
for _ and against _ the presumably hearty souls roughing it for a
shot at $1 million. By BILL GOODYKOONTZ. Story will move in the
``E'' category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
